        "text_KJR9AE": {
          "type": "text",
          "name": "t:names.text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Spot Clean First: Most marks can be removed with a damp cloth and mild soap. Give it a quick wipe instead of a full wash whenever possible.<br/><br/>Machine Wash (If Needed): For a deeper clean, wash separately on a gentle cold cycle. Use mild detergent and do not bleach.<br/></p><p>Drying: Air dry flat in the shade. Do not tumble dry, as heat may damage the quilted padding or waterproof base.<br/></p><p>Storage: Make sure your blanket is completely dry before folding and storing. Keep it in a cool, dry place to prevent mould or odours.<br/></p><p>No Ironing or Dry Cleaning: Heat and harsh chemicals can weaken the waterproof underside and reduce the blanket’s durability.</p>",
